SWABLU has light and fluffy wings that
are like cottony clouds. This POKMON
is not frightened of people. It lands on the heads of people and
sits there like a cotton-fluff hat.

SWABLU loves to make things clean.
If it spots something dirty, it will wipe
and polish it with its cottony wings. If its wings become dirty, this POKMON
finds a stream and showers itself.
